items.title: Pterostylis smaragdyna
items.content_text: Many tens of plants both flowering and sterile. Higher density than observed in past.

items.title: Crassula muscosa var. muscosa
items.content_text: An well-established patch of succulent weed, which has originated from the entrance of a property on the east side of Bacchus Marsh-Balliang Road, and now spread across to the opposite side of the road and into private property. Infestation appears to be contained within a single patch, but has spread to approximately 30m along the roadside.

items.title: Ozothamnus obcordatus
items.content_text: Small flowering individual growing through Lomandra.

items.title: Eriochilus cucullatus s.s.
items.content_text: With a loose patch of about 8 other plants (flowering and in bud), growing at the immediate edge of the bitumen road through the spill of the basalt stones and bitumen.

items.title: Olearia pannosa subsp. cardiophylla
items.content_text: A young plant - evidence of recruitment at this population.

items.title: Olearia pannosa subsp. cardiophylla
items.content_text: Severely browsed by wallabies. One of only two plants of this species found in the near vicinity. The plant was caged to protect from Wallaby browsing. The other plant is also caged and approximately 30 metres away.

items.title: Olearia pannosa subsp. cardiophylla
items.content_text: One of only two plants of this species found in the near vicinity. The plant was caged to protect from Wallaby browsing. The other plant is also caged and approximately 30 metres away.

items.title: Pomaderris prunifolia var. prunifolia
items.content_text: Isolated mature plant. Only one other observed nearby.

items.title: Pultenaea graveolens
items.content_text: Dense patch of young plants up to 1m tall.

items.title: Tetratheca ciliata
items.content_text: Unusual and rare pure-white flowering form of this species. Only a single plant observed among many typical flowered plants.

items.title: Glossodia major
items.content_text: Patch of numerous Glossodia major in flower along track beside road.

items.title: Sambucus gaudichaudiana
items.content_text: Growing in protected areas between rocks.
